Fuvg Unccraf.
%
Rng fuvg -- ovyyvbaf bs syvrf pna'g or jebat.
%
	Jryy, chax vf xvaq bs nagv-rguvpny, naljnl.  Vgf rguvpf, fb gb fcrnx,
vapyhqr n qvfqnva sbe rguvpf va trareny.  Vs lbh unir gb guvax nobhg fbzr-
guvat fb uneq, gura vg'f ohyyfuvg naljnl; gung'f gur vqrn.  Chaxf ner nagv-
vfzvfgf, gb pbva n grez.  Ohg abarguryrff, gurl unir n cerggl pyrneyl qrsvarq
fgnapr naq vzntr, naq GUNG vf jung jr unat gur grez `chax' ba.
		-- Wrss T. Obar
%
Genvyvat Rqtr Grpuabybtvrf vf cyrnfrq gb naabhapr gur sbyybjvat
GRGsynzr cebtenzzr:

1) Sbe n artbgvngrq cevpr (ab dhngybbf npprcgrq) bar bs bhe synzvat
   ercerfragngvirf jvyy synzr gur yvivat fuvg bhg bs gur cbfgre bs
   lbhe pubvpr. Gur cevpr vf vairefyl cebcbegvbany gb ubj zhpu bs
   na nffubyr gur gnetrg vg. Jr pnaabg or pbaivaprq gb synzr Qraavf
   Evgpuvr. Zngg Penjsbeq synzrf ner serr.

2) Sbe n artbgvngrq cevpr (fnzr neenatrzrag) gur GRGsynzr cebtenzzr
   vf bssrevat ``synzr vafherapr''. Haqre guvf neenatrzrag, vs
   bar bs bhe cbyvpl ubyqref vf synzrq, jr jvyy pnapry gur bssraqvat
   negvpyr naq synzr gur synzre, gb n pevfc.

3) Gur GRGsynzr synzvat ercerfragngvirf vapyhqr: Evpuneq Frkgba, Byrt
   Xvfnyri, Qvnar Ubyg, Gevfu B'Gnhzn, Qnir Uvyy, Tert Abjnx naq bhe zbfg
   erprag ndhvfvgvba, Xrvgu Qblyr. Ohg nyy ur jvyy qb vf chg lbh va uvf
   xvyy svyr. Jrrzon ol fcrpvny neenatrzrag.

		-- Evpuneq Frkgba
%
"Jryy, vg qba'g znxr gur fha fuvar, ohg ng yrnfg vg qba'g qrrcra gur fuvg."
		-- Fgenvgre Rzcl, va _Evqqyrl_Jnyxre_ ol Ehffryy Ubona
